 For intermediate values of risk aversion, 
\begin_inset Formula $0.5<\sigma<1$
\end_inset

, facts 1-3 above continue to hold (fact 2 in a neighborhood of 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma=1$
\end_inset

).
 In addition, for 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

